      "span_text": "A 820-bp fragment of the MC1R gene was amplified using the following primers MSHR72 (5¢-ATGCCAGTGAGGGCAACCA-3¢) and MSHR9 (5¢-CTGGCTCCGGAAGGCATAGAT-3¢)  ."
